title: China 30 Year bond-Yield
description: China 30 Year Bond Yield was 3.11 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the China 30 Year bond-Yield reached an all time high of 5.25 in January of 2014. This page includes a chart with historical data for China 30Y.
